ine release; anti-inflammatory.','Atopic dermatitis, eczema.','Local irritation, burning, pruritus.','Hypersensitivity, immunosuppressed patients.',0,0,'Apply thin layer to affected area twice daily','Twice daily','2025-08-23 13:25:58','2025-08-23 13:25:58','Apply thin layer twice daily','Twice daily',NULL,NULL,'Use cautiously in children under 2','Twice daily',NULL,NULL),(231,'Antispasmodic','Otilonium Bromide','Inhibits gastrointestinal smooth muscle contractions by blocking calcium channels.','Irritable bowel syndrome (IBS), abdominal cramps.','Constipation, dry mouth, mild nausea.','Hypersensitivity to otilonium or anticholinergic drugs.',1,1,'40 mg tablet orally three times daily before meals','TID before meals','2025-08-23 13:25:58','2025-08-23 13:25:58','40 mg three times daily','TID',NULL,NULL,'Not recommended for children under 12',NULL,NULL,NULL),(232,'Prokinetic / Anti-nausea','Domperidone','Dopamine D2 receptor antagonist; enhances gastrointestinal motility and reduces nausea/vomiting.','Gastroparesis, nausea, vomiting.','Dry mouth, abdominal cramps, headache, dizziness.','Prolactinoma, hypersensitivity, QT prolongation.',1,1,'10 mg orally 3–4 times daily 15–30 min before meals','3–4 times daily','2025-08-23 13:25:58','2025-08-23 13:25:58','10 mg 3–4 times daily before meals','3–4 times daily',NULL,NULL,'Not recommended for children under 12',NULL,NULL,NULL),(233,'Gastroprotective agent','Sucralfate','Forms a protective barrier over ulcers, preventing acid damage.','Peptic ulcers, gastritis.','Constipation, nausea.','Hypersensitivity, renal failure caution.',1,1,'1 g orally 4 times daily on empty stomach','4 times daily','2025-08-23 13:25:58','2025-08-23 13:25:58','1 g 4 times daily','4 times daily',NULL,NULL,'Not recommended in children under 6',NULL,NULL,NULL),(234,'Topical skin protectant / Humectant','Dexpanthenol','Converted to pantothenic acid; promotes skin regeneration and hydration.','Minor burns, wounds, dry skin, diaper rash.','Rare local irritation or redness.','Hypersensitivity to dexpanthenol.',1,1,'Apply thin layer 1–2 times daily','1–2 times daily','2025-08-23 13:25:58','2025-08-23 13:25:58','Apply thin layer 1–2 times daily','1–2 times daily',NULL,NULL,'Safe for children and infants','1–2 times daily',NULL,NULL),(235,'Topical emollient / Moisturizer','Almond oil | Glycerol | Beeswax','Moisturizes and protects skin, promotes barrier function.','Dry skin, mild eczema, chapped skin.','Rare skin irritation or allergy.','Hypersensitivity to any component.',1,1,'Apply thin layer 1–3 times daily as needed','1–3 times daily','2025-08-23 13:25:58','2025-08-23 13:25:58','Apply thin layer 1–3 times daily','1–3 times daily',NULL,NULL,'Safe for children','1–3 times daily',NULL,NULL),(236,'Topical skin protectant / Healing agent','Sesame Oil | Cactus Extract | Beeswax','Promotes skin healing, moisturizes, and protects from infection.','Minor burns, scars, dry or damaged skin.','Rare irritation or redness.','Hypersensitivity to any component.',1,1,'Apply thin layer 2–3 times daily','2–3 times daily','2025-08-23 13:25:58','2025-08-23 13:25:58','Apply thin layer 2–3 times daily','2–3 times daily',NULL,NULL,'Safe for children','2–3 times daily',NULL,NULL),(237,'Topical soothing agent / Moisturizer','Aloe Vera','Provides hydration, anti-inflammatory and wound-healing properties.','Burns, minor cuts, dry skin, irritation.','Rare local irritation.','Hypersensitivity to aloe.',1,1,'Apply gel thinly 2–3 times daily','2–3 times daily','2025-08-23 13:25:58','2025-08-23 13:25:58','Apply gel thinly 2–3 times daily','2–3 times daily',NULL,NULL,'Safe for children','2–3 times daily',NULL,NULL);
